project_descr: Culture and Heritage for Social and Economic Development Joint Programme

donor_name: UNDP AS AA FOR JP PASS THROUGH
outputs.output_descr: The CHSED JP is built upon five achievable outcomes and based on national, sub-national and sectoral priorities for culture and development. Interventions include the provision of policy support, improvement of capacities in the field of the protection, promotion and management of cultural assets, safeguarding of the most valuable cultural heritage monuments and sites, and strengthening the cultural industries sector for socio-economic development and achievement of the MDGs.

project_title: culture and heritage for social and economic development
